\c 3
\s Kuparidza kwaJohwani Mubhabhatidzi
\p
\v 1 Pamazuva iwayo kwakauya Johwani Mubhabhatidzi, achiparidza murenje reJudhiya,
\v 2 achiti: Tendeukai; nokuti ushe hwekumatenga hwaswedera.
\v 3 Nokuti uyu ndiye wakarehwa nezvake naIsaya muporofita, achiti: Inzwi rounodanidzira murenje: Gadzirirai mugwagwa waShe, ruramisai nzira dzake.
\v 4 Iyezve Johwani waiva nenguvo yake yamambava ekamera nebhanhire redehwe pachiuno chake; nechikafu chake chaiva mhashu nouchi hwedondo.
\v 5 Zvino kwakabudira kwaari Jerusarema neJudhiya rose nedunhu rose rakapoteredza Jorodhani;
\v 6 vakabhabhatidzwa naye muna Joridhani vachireurura zvivi zvavo.
\p
\v 7 Asi wakati achiona vazhinji vavaFarisi navaSadhusi vachiuya kurubhabhatidzo rwake akati kwavari: Zvizvarwa zvenyoka, ndianiko wakakutaridzirai kuti mutize hasha dzinouya?
\v 8 Naizvozvo berekai zvibereko zvakafanira kutendeuka.
\v 9 Musafunga kutaura mukati menyu \add muchiti\add*: Tina Abhurahamu baba; nokuti ndinoti kwamuri: Mwari unokwanisa kubva pamabwe awa kumutsira Abhurahamu vana.
\v 10 Ikozvino sanhuwo ratoiswa pamudzi wemiti, naizvozvo muti umwe noumwe usingabereki zvibereko zvakanaka unotemwa ugokandirwa mumoto.
\v 11 Ini zvirokwazvo ndinokubhabhatidzai nemvura \add mupinde\add* mukutendeuka; asi uyo unouya shure kwangu unesimba kupfuura ini, wandisina kufanira kutakura shangu dzake; iye uchakubhabhatidzai noMweya Mutsvene nomoto.
\v 12 Une rusero rwuri muruoko rwake, uchatsvaira buriro rake kwazvo, agounganidzira zviyo zvake mudura, asi hundi ucha\add i\add*pisa nemoto usingadzimiki.
\s Kubhabhatidzwa kwaJesu
\p
\v 13 Ipapo Jesu wakabva Garirea akasvika paJoridhani kuna Johwani, kuti abhabhatidzwe naye.
\v 14 Asi Johwani wakamurambidza achiti: Ndini ndinoda kubhabhatidzwa nemwi, asi imwi mouya kwandiri?
\v 15 Asi Jesu achipindura wakati kwaari: Tenda ikozvino, nokuti saizvozvo zvakatifanira kuti tizadzise kururama kose. Ipapo akamutendera.
\v 16 Asi Jesu, wakati abhabhatidzwa, akakwira pakarepo \add achibva\add* mumvura; zvino tarira, matenga akamuzarukira, akaona Mweya waMwari achiburuka senjiva, achiuya pamusoro pake.
\v 17 Zvino tarira, inzwi rachibva kumatenga richiti: Uyu ndiye Mwanakomana wangu unodikamwa, wandinofadzwa naye kwazvo.
